default2.1
default              
defaultWe fully support the continuing and enduring role and public purposes of the BBC. The BBC is the cornerstone of public service broadcasting and media, going further than other broadcasters and complementing what others provide.  This is partly as a result 
defaultof its unique funding model, which provides a critical mass of investment that should allow proper risk taking.   As an invaluable cultural asset to the UK, it is an internationally recognised example of what British creativity and commitment can achieve. 
default Like the organisations and individuals that the Arts Council funds, the BBC can take risks that the commercial market cannot. 
