defaultl, educational and creative purpose. To this end more should be done to encourage the BBC to work with a greater number and variety of partner
defaults – as exemplified by The Space. The BBC should
default not only to commission content
default from other public providers
default but act
defaultively host and promote
default. 
defaultThis is an important manifestation of the future BBC’s technology and innovation remit – leading on establishing technical standards, developing and backing open platforms and standards, and facilitating the greater reach of other p
defaultublic service content providers from the arts.
